<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Sohn</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-07 13:53:48</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The halbeard (sic.) is not really a very good weapon. I got it from a skeleton as a newbie (lvl 1 even) and used it fo a long time. As long as you hit sometimesits worth it, as it does twice as much damage as the newbie weapon, for just a bit higher delay. Once you reach lvl 4 tho, you will want a Mino Battle Axe, or similar, and the Halbeard is uesless. Good for nothing really, exept for extreme newbies.</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
