<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: cayton</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-18 09:23:00</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>i agree.  i first got one of these from a player in erudin.  (you cant buy them in erudin)  it is a sweet weapon for a newbie, and i would say it is the best rusty weapon.  i used it till about level 6, maybe 7, because in erudin its hard to get others.  but i would suggest it to any level 1-6 players.</font></td></tr></table>
